DESIGN DIRECTION
Use a premium enterprise SaaS design inspired by Stripe, Linear, Ramp, Workday, Vanta, Retool, Rippling, and Mercury.
The UI should feel structured, intelligent, audit-ready, compliance-aware, and workflow-oriented.
Avoid excessive glassmorphism, cartoon illustrations, neon Web3 styling, NFT wallet aesthetics, or playful startup visuals.

Suggested palette:
- Primary: #4F46E5
- Primary Dark: #312E81
- Accent: #7C3AED
- Background: #F8FAFC
- Surface: #FFFFFF
- Border: #E2E8F0
- Text Primary: #0F172A
- Text Secondary: #475569
- Success: #10B981
- Warning: #F59E0B
- Danger: #EF4444
